  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/3385",
  "title": "Panel should receive the same render options than the wrapped widget",
  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe 🙏**\r\n\r\nThe current implementation of `panel` receives the raw results inside the `hidden` option. It makes it very difficult for users to implement the removed option `autoHideContainer`.\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like 🤔**\r\n\r\nWe should investigate how we could provide the render options of the connector directly rather than the raw results.\r\n\r\n**Describe alternatives you've considered ✨**\r\n\r\nNone at the moment.\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\n\r\n> https://secure.helpscout.net/conversation/741036895/113536\r\n",
